channel.title: June 27, 2013, my 5th year on mopar!
channel.description:
My fifth year here at mopar scape is two days away, what year are you on? Where you active the whole time?
Just a little conversation starter :p
No flame, hate, lies, or absolute bullshit, I can look you know. :)
